trans-unit.source: Indico EPayment Plugin for SixPay services
trans-unit.target: Indico EPayment Plugin for SixPay服务。

trans-unit.source: Once installed, it can be enabled in the administrator and event settings. Configuration uses the same options for global defaults and event specific overrides.
trans-unit.target: 安装后,可以在管理员和事件设置中启用。配置对全局默认值和事件特定覆盖使用相同的选项。

trans-unit.source: Plugin for the Indico event management system to use EPayment via SIX Payment services.
trans-unit.target: Indico事件管理系统的插件,通过SIX支付服务使用EP支付。
